  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Quantification of interferon-γ produced by specific CD8+ (cluster of differentiation 8) T cells after ex-vivo stimulation with various CMV epitopes using the commercial assay QuantiFeron®- CMV</measure>
    <time_frame>up to 12 months from transplant</time_frame>
    <description>Quantiferon® is assessed multiple times and it will be considered positive when first positive test is assessed.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
