    <measure>Measurement of overall immune response by determination of the activity of CD4+ (cluster of differentiation 4) T cells</measure>
    <time_frame>up to 12 months from transplant</time_frame>
    <description>InmunKnow® is assessed multiple times and it will be considered positive when first positive test is assessed.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
